{"tid":1549361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣書店眾籌19小時達標","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:18:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"218d78b16f4f58e7edfc8f1cde68f3802a732e9f","tid":1549361,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190907/20763762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F20763762&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a906c532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F20763762&h=96b1e7ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190907/20763762</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣書店眾籌19小時達標<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190907/large/1567786074_6075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190907%2Flarge%2F1567786074_6075.jpg&h=39820fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林榮基<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】已停業近四年的香港銅鑼灣書店，有望在台北復活。前店長林榮基初步選址在台北西門町復辦書店，為此發起目標280萬元新台幣（下同，約70.4萬港元）的網上眾籌。眾籌在周四晚8時啟動，結果昨日下午3時半不到已達標。林對眾籌迅速超標完成坦言「有點意外、很高興」，預計半年內確定店址，期待書店明年中能正式開幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擬明年台北重開<br />\n<br />\n今年4月因港府計劃修訂《逃犯條例》流亡台灣的林榮基，此前一直有在台北復辦銅鑼灣書店的想法。眾籌計劃前晚在台灣網上募款平台flyingv正式啟動，目標為280萬元，期限為60天，結果啟動19.5小時後即告達標。昨在嘉義出席座談會的林說：「銅鑼灣書店在香港做不到的事，或被禁止的事，將在自由的台灣，進行下去。」募資平台頁面顯示，募得資金六成將用於書店進書，兩成半用於裝修，一成作為前期租金資金，餘下5%為雜項開支。若眾籌金額超出280萬元，部份將作為後續營運資金，主要用於舉辦交流活動。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基稱：「每一位珍惜自由民主的人們，一起成為書店精神意義上的『股東』，自此銅鑼灣書店是屬於自由台灣、自由香港所有。」flyingV募資平台品牌總監呂岱芸說，眾籌快速達標顯示台灣民眾很關注香港反送中議題。林曾受《蘋果新聞網》採訪表示，香港已是他回不去、也不願回去的故鄉。<br />\n<br />\n記者陳嘯軒 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n習頭馬蔡奇遭照肺後變口吃<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n嚴刑逼供致殘 母暴斃妻改嫁  被屈謀殺坐冤獄23載  吉林男獲賠500萬"},{"pid":"d362e2503d952efda9bd56560b83078b80eaf740","tid":1549361,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"十分鐘，了解《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549355</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac714265c2cdf6428f943575c8a9fa1146a2ade2","tid":1549361,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339cdefc79dc1ffccc2efb9a3749b929e54d705f","tid":1549361,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"冇眾籌link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffacf11090874f3c770b5c30f4bbe02e4a5ffc9","tid":1549361,"uid":1360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"習頭馬蔡奇遭照肺後變口吃&lt;&mdash;&mdash;反而對呢個有性趣，有無link？"},{"pid":"f31b06deb724937c4aca2219285d1eba02464215","tid":1549361,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港人最多就係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5576cba82af4d6211c6e896d1211f6a053e5c9dd","tid":1549361,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339cdefc79dc1ffccc2efb9a3749b929e54d705f","tid":1549361,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"冇眾籌link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"完左"},{"pid":"0a52256b73ad3f30f7ebe751e53e568cb6d79ffb","tid":1549361,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:18:48.000Z"